script.name: plugin.guilds.patch
script.sourceplaintext:
$Guild.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data'
if $a.version == 'asteroid' $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y gosub sub.DoAsteroids end end
else if $a.version == 'NewHome' $sector = get sector from universe index: x=23, y=0 if $sector -> exists $table = $sector ->get station table from sector if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $key ->disable ship rebuild $key ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end $table = $sector ->get sector custom objects if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $key ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end $array = $sector ->get wreck array if $array $i = size of array $array while $i dec $i = $key = $array[$i] $key ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] $sector ->remove sector wreck: $key end end $sector -> clear all wrecks $sector ->set sector text id: 15016 $sector ->set sector description id: 15016 load universe map: 'patch_newhome' end
else if $a.version == 8 $sector = get sector from universe index: x=7, y=16 if $sector -> exists $owner = $sector -> get owner race if $owner == Yaki $table = $sector ->get station table from sector if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $owner = $key -> get owner race skip if $owner == Pirates $key ->set owner race to Yaki $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end end end
$sector = get sector from universe index: x=20, y=13 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Shipyard race=Teladi flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null if $station -> exists $type = Free Argon Trading Station $station ->remove product from factory or dock: $type $type = Teladi Trading Station $station ->add product to factory or dock: $type $type = Mammoth $station ->remove product from factory or dock: $type end end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=20, y=14 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Shipyard race=Teladi flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null if $station -> exists $type = Mammoth $station ->remove product from factory or dock: $type end end
else if $a.version == 12 $sector = get sector from universe index: x=8, y=5 if $sector -> exists $aShips = find ship: sector=$sector class or type=Shadowblade race=Guilds flags=[Find.Multiple] refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=100 refpos=null if is datatype[ $aShips ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $i = size of array $aShips while $i dec $i = $ship = $aShips[$i] $ship ->set owner race to Privateer end else if $aShips -> exists $aShips ->set owner race to Privateer end end
else if $a.version == 11 $sector = get sector from universe index: x=4, y=2 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Teladi Space Equipment Dock race=Teladi flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null do if $station -> exists $station ->add product to factory or dock: Salvage Claim Software end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=9, y=8 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Teladi Space Equipment Dock race=Teladi flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null do if $station -> exists $station ->add product to factory or dock: Salvage Claim Software end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=20, y=9 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Teladi Space Equipment Dock race=Teladi flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null do if $station -> exists $station ->add product to factory or dock: Salvage Claim Software end
else if $a.version == 10 $hq = $Guild.Data['assassin']['hq'] if $hq $hq = $hq['obj'] if $hq -> exists if $hq -> is of class Ship $speaker = $hq ->get pilot speaker if not $speaker @ = $hq -> call script lib.cycrow.createspeaker : Race=Paranid end end end end
else if $a.version == 9 $owner = Pioneer $sector = get sector from universe index: x=23, y=0 if $sector -> exists gosub sub.ChangeSectorOwner $sector ->set sector to core security [TRUE] $sector ->set sector music track: 6015 $sector ->set sector music fixed: [TRUE] end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=22, y=0 do if $sector -> exists gosub sub.ChangeStationOwner $sector = get sector from universe index: x=23, y=1 do if $sector -> exists gosub sub.ChangeSectorOwner $sector = get sector from universe index: x=23, y=2 do if $sector -> exists gosub sub.ChangeSectorOwner $sector = get sector from universe index: x=23, y=3 if $sector -> exists gosub sub.ChangeSectorOwner $sector ->set sector to core security [TRUE] $sector ->set capital sector: [TRUE] end
else if $a.version == 7 $tmp = 'asteroid' @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.patch : Version=$tmp Delay=0
if $Guild.Data['assassin']['member'] $guild.level = $Guild.Data['assassin']['level'] if $guild.level > 5 $exp = $Guild.Data['assassin']['exp'] send script event: name='guild.assassin.level', object=[PLAYERSHIP], param1=$guild.level, param2=$exp end end
else if $a.version == 6 $tmp = 'asteroid' @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.patch : Version=$tmp Delay=0
$sector = get sector from universe index: x=19, y=13 if $sector -> exists $flags = [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.Hyperspeed] $gate = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if $gate -> exists $gate ->set rotation: alpha=32768 beta=0 gamma=0 end end
else if $a.version == 5 $hq = $Guild.Data['merc']['hq'] if $hq $array.sales = $hq['sales'] $guild.level = $Guild.Data['merc']['level'] $hq = $hq['obj'] if $hq -> exists $hq ->set override name id: 89030 do if $Guild.Data['merc']['member'] @ = $hq -> call script plugin.guilds.adjusthq : Guild Level=$guild.level Sales Data=$array.sales end end $hq = $Guild.Data['merc']['shipyard'] if $hq $hq = $hq['obj'] do if $hq -> exists $hq ->set override name id: 91563 end
$military = $Guild.Data['military.argon'] if $military $military['agent'] = 152 $military['agent.greet'] = 100200 $military['agent.resign'] = 100201 $military['agent.page'] = 121 $military['agent.face'] = 102 end $military = $Guild.Data['military.terran'] if $military $military['agent'] = 152 $military['agent.greet'] = 110004 $military['agent.resign'] = 110005 $military['agent.page'] = 125 $military['agent.face'] = 1133 $ranks = $military['ranks'] $military[1] = 11001 $military[2] = 11002 $military[3] = 11003 $military[4] = 11004 $military[5] = 11005 $military[6] = 11006 $military[7] = 11007 $military[8] = 11008 $military[9] = 11009 $military[10] = 11010 end
$x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y gosub sub.DoAsteroids end end
$sector = get sector from universe index: x=12, y=15 if $sector -> exists $shipyard = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Argon Federal Argon Shipyard race=Paranid flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null if $shipyard -> exists $x = $shipyard -> get x position $y = $shipyard -> get y position $z = $shipyard -> get z position $station = $shipyard gosub sub.DestroyStation $shipyard = create station: type=Paranid Paranid Shipyard owner=Paranid addto=$sector x=$x y=$y z=$z $ware = Paranid Low-yield Sidearms Fab $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Paranid Station Upgrade Kit L $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Deimos $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Medusa $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Perseus $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pericles $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pericles Vanguard $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Theseus $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pegasus $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Helios $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Snotra $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Hermes $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware end end $sector = get sector from universe index: x=3, y=4 if $sector -> exists $station = find station: sector=$sector class or type=Argon Federal Argon Shipyard race=Pirates flags=null refobj=null maxdist=null maxnum=null refpos=null if $station -> exists $x = $station -> get x position $y = $station -> get y position $z = $station -> get z position gosub sub.DestroyStation $shipyard = create station: type=Pirates Pirate Shipyard owner=Pirates addto=$sector x=$x y=$y z=$z $ware = Pirates Station Upgrade Kit S $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirates Station Upgrade Kit M $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirates Incendiary Bomb Launcher Forge $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirates Plasma Burst Generator Forge $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Base $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Anarchy Port $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Yamato $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Galleon $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Brigantine $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Carrack $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Marauder $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Orinoco $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Centaur $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Osprey $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Eclipse $shipyard ->add product to $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Blastclaw Prototype $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Advanced Eclipse $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Buster $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Buzzard Vanguard $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Elite $shipyard ->add Raider $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Harrier Vanguard $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Kestrel $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Mobile Pirate Station $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Caravel $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Pirate Ship $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Polacca Armoured Transporter $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware $ware = Tepukei $shipyard ->add product to factory or dock: $ware end end end return null
sub.DoAsteroids: if $sector -> exists $table = $sector ->get asteroid table from sector if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $asteroid = $key $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key $ware = $asteroid -> get resource waretype of asteroid if $ware == Metal Alloys OR $ware == Silicon Wafers $waretype = $asteroid -> get ware type code of object $subtype = get subtype of ware $waretype $yield = $asteroid -> get asteroid yield $pos.x = $asteroid -> get x position $pos.y = $asteroid -> get y position $pos.z = $asteroid -> get z position $is.scanned = $asteroid -> is asteroid scanned $rot.alpha = $asteroid -> get rot alpha $rot.beta = $asteroid -> get rot beta $rot.gamma = $asteroid -> get rot gamma $cansee.hidden = $asteroid ->can see hidden wares (Asteroids) $hidden.wares = $asteroid ->get asteroid hidden wares table $is.known = $asteroid -> is known if $hidden.wares $hidde.wares.points = table alloc $h.ware = get next key: table=$hidden.wares key=null while $h.ware $points = $asteroid ->get asteroid hidden ware discovery points: ware=$h.ware $hidde.wares.points[$h.ware] = $points $h.ware = get next key: table=$hidden.wares key=$h.ware end end $points = $asteroid ->get discovery points $asteroid ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] skip if $yield > 0 $yield = random value from 1 to 10 - 1 if $ware == Metal Alloys $asteroid = create asteroid: type=$subtype addto=$sector resource=5 yield=$yield x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z else $asteroid = create asteroid: type=$subtype addto=$sector resource=9 yield=$yield x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z end if $asteroid -> exists $asteroid ->set known status to $is.known $asteroid ->set asteroid scanned to $is.scanned $asteroid ->set rotation: alpha=$rot.alpha beta=$rot.beta gamma=$rot.gamma $asteroid ->set can see hidden wares (Asteroids): $cansee.hidden $asteroid ->set discovery points: points=$points if $hidden.wares $ware = get next key: table=$hidden.wares key=null while $ware $amt = $hidden.wares[$ware] $points = $hidde.wares.points[$ware] $asteroid ->add asteroid hidden ware: ware=$ware, amount=$amt, discovery points=$points $ware = get next key: table=$hidden.wares key=$ware end end end end end end end endsub
sub.ChangeSectorOwner: $sector ->set owner race to $owner $table = $sector ->get gate array: include hyperspeed=[FALSE] gosub sub.ChangeOwner gosub sub.ChangeStationOwner endsub
sub.ChangeStationOwner: $table = $sector ->get station table from sector gosub sub.ChangeOwner endsub
sub.ChangeOwner: if $table if is datatype[ $table ] == DATATYPE_TABLE $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $check.owner = $key -> get owner race do if $check.owner != Player $key ->set owner race to $owner $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end else if is datatype[ $table ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $key.i = size of array $table while $key.i dec $key.i = $key = $table[$key.i] $check.owner = $key -> get owner race do if $check.owner != Player $key ->set owner race to $owner end end endsub
sub.DestroyStation: $pause = [FALSE] $aShips = $station -> get ship array from sector/ship/station if $aShips $i = size of array $aShips while $i dec $i = $s = $aShips[$i] $owner = $s -> get owner race if $owner == Player @ START $s -> call script !move.undock : $pause = [TRUE] end end end do if $pause @ = wait 500 ms $station ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] endsub return null
